About I Am Real Hip Hop

HIP HOP is a state of mind that erupted out of urban areas and has proliferated the globe. At IAmReal.HIPHOP we are curators of the golden area of HIP HOP and vanguards of the evolution of the current culture while staying true to the roots. We are not of the mindset that all new HIP HOP is garbage, we are just in search of good music, artistry and thought leaders that will help the culture progress...
